START_DATE: Optional[str] = None  # e.g., "2024-01-01"
END_DATE: Optional[str] = None    # e.g., "2024-12-31"# IB Range Breakout Backtest (CSV)

This notebook backtests a simple Initial Balance (IB) breakout strategy on intraday CSV data.

What it does:
- Loads CSV with OHLCV and timestamps
- Computes per-day IB (High/Low/Mid/Delta) for a given window (e.g., 09:30–10:30)
- Trades the first breakout after the IB window with TP = 1× IB range and SL = opposite IB edge (configurable)
- Exits at session end if neither TP/SL are hit
- Reports metrics, equity curve, and drawdown

You only need to set the CSV path and, if necessary, column names/timezone below.